snippet.title: I Survived 100 Days in a Zombie Apocalypse Enchanted World Hardcore… Here’s What Happened
snippet.description:
I Survived 100 Days in a Zombie Apocalypse Enchanted World Hardcore… Here’s What Happened...

Check Out my Better Minecraft Plus Video:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o97_IJ3KFDE

In this video I am surviving 100 days in a zombie apocalypse world, filled with unknown creatures and monsters... I will try to face my fears against the unknown ahead... Hopefully I make it...
The Modpack is Better Minecraft, with 40+ mods added by me to enhance and make the world filled with unknown and dangerous creatures and buildings...

1:11 - 1-10
9:23 - 10-30
20:32 - 30-40
26:20 - 40-60
34:40 - 60-90
42:40 - 90-99
48:25 - 100

Big Thanks To Sharkie!  
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_rqYJKLbTjZ294DT9FG3xg
Sharkie's YouTube ^^^^^^^

Better Minecraft Modpack:
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/better-minecraft-modpack

One Of The Zombies Modpack:
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/zombie-extreme

This video took over 60 hours to complete in total, you have no clue how thankful I would be if you'd just push the subscribe button, Notification bell, and like the video. Thank you for everything that you have done :)
